What's new in this update:

• Import a theme by pasting it, choosing a .json file, or from a link — now in a full-screen editor that's easy to review before importing.
• Cleaner, calmer Settings and Personalization screens.
• New option to hide the auto-updating "latest" AI models and show only specific versions in the picker.
• Fixed imported themes that could vanish after a restart.

Thanks for testing this alpha!
